<quantity box="[678,798,476,503]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.25" metricValueMax="2.5" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" unit="m" value="22.5" valueMax="25.0" valueMin="20.0">
20 to 
<specimenCount box="[739,798,476,503]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" type="generic">25 m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
. The scarcity of records could be explained by the species preferred habitat in the archipelago. This ophiuroid appears to live mainly on soft bottoms at depths between 20 and 
<specimenCount box="[151,229,548,575]" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" type="generic">
<quantity box="[151,224,548,575]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.58" pageId="52" pageNumber="53" unit="m" value="458.0">458 m</quantity>
